					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You basically cannot use a atmega/pic microcontroller to emulate a mapper. You'll need to respond to bus activity in 1/(1.789773 MHz for NTSC)=558ns minus the speed of the ROMs you're using.<br /><br />At 8MHz, that's going from &quot;discovering there's a new value on the bus&quot; to &quot;driving the correct value&quot; in about 3 instructions.</div>

