t 8MHz, that's going from &quot;discovering there's a new value on the bus&quot; to &quot;driving the correct value&quot; in about 3 instructions.</div><br />The cycle/opcode is 1 or 2 depending on the opcode.<br /><br />Which microcontroller could be able to do this?</div>

