				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p143470">Re: Is it possible to develop a mapper by using an ATMEGA?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=143470#p143470"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Fri Mar 20, 2015 4:32 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
